<br>
Most of the time when i draw i draw because i'm bored out of my mind and it starts coming up with ideas and i throw them on paper or i sing or something to let it out. Other times I'm listening to a song or watching tv with a pad of paper in front of me just doodling...<br>
<br>
Just don't let your teachers know you watch tv while drawing..in fact in one of the books i have one of the rules of most of the great disney and WB artists is &quot;I'm not smart enough to draw and listen to music at the same time..&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#CCCCCC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/bpolykarbonbbs.showUserPublicProfile?gid=architect@polykarbonbbs>Architect</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Karbonite</span><br> <font color=#336699>(7/23/03 6:36 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=12566.topic&index=18>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: re:</span><hr size=1> hehe sweet ideas guys <br>
